fixed Content-Length body -> 200 exact
chunked multi-chunk (ext + trailers, split reads) -> 200 exact
chunked single chunk -> 200 exact
Content-Length over max_body -> 413 (early)
chunked body over max_body -> 413 (early)
Content-Length + Transfer-Encoding -> 400
Transfer-Encoding: gzip -> 501
malformed chunk (bad hex) -> 400
malformed chunk (missing CRLF) -> 400
malformed chunk (0x-prefix size) -> 400
chunk size over max_body -> 413
mid-body disconnect -> clean close, slot freed
server healthy after run
no leak: net-zero allocations after request-body handling
ok
